A horror modpack based around protecting yourself in your home while the terror reigned outside your home in the night occasionally attacking you.
This modpack includes multiple horror-based entities like John, Zorro's Monsters, and the elusive Herobrine. Herobrine will always spawn in your world so get ready for some unwanted spooks!

Every 10 nights, an invasion will begin forcing players to defend their territory. You also have to keep track of your sanity and the occasional nightmares you may get.
Explorations is also a must in this world, explore the world for better protection and bases!
